<br />
<br />I pulled a copy of the original NES simon belmont sprite set for size comparison for making another set of character sprites. (Don't worry, they will be all original, I just need a size.) --Should anyone want to do a castlevania type clone. Considering pimping out my magician (see left!) for that role, but not sure how he will work out at that scale, and in reduced colors.
