		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />*double checks*
<br />
<br />Yeah,  I suppose it is oblique projection. (shrug)
<br />
<br />Regardless, it's there, it's free, and it uses around 9 tiles.  (some of the tiles in the sample's bottom are not used in the sample. they are included for "finishing series" when put next to solid colors, or for use with combining with another tile using a logical AND, such as against a sky tile.)
<br />
<br />It's just something different from the stock 2D platformer (megaman, Mario), or Zelda-Like overhead flat projections.
<br />
<br />For completeness, I need to make "archway", "Door", and "steps" tiles though. Might do that tomorrow.

		

